long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Screen sharing extension for FreeConference.com

Share your screen from your FreeConference.com online meeting room with a click of a button. FreeConference.com is a free web conferencing and conference call service. 

No downloads required. Simply share your URL and connect.

Other FREE FreeConference.com Features:
- Meet face-to-face with video chat
- Share documents
- Text chat and save notes for later
- Conference call with up to 400 people by phone
- Schedule in advance or start a meeting on demand

Don't have an account? Sign-up free at www.freeconference.com !
